data.description: Fully Equipped 3 Bed 2 Bath Home in one of the most desirable areas in Lakeside, Corner lot ,Cathedral ceilings Kitchen granite counters with stainless steel appliances, New paint throughout, New tall baseboards, with several Smart features like, LiftMaster Wi-Fi, Led Garage door opener with camera, ADT security system ,Wi-Fi door bell & pool camera,Motion sensor, Door  &  window sensors. Water way-Variable speed pool pump, Pentair FNS plus- NEW Pool filter, NEW Carrier 2 stage heating and AC System. Installed in 2022 with warranty, NeEW Roof installed in 2022 with a 30 yr warranty, NEW Fully paid Solar installed in October of 2022 with a 25 yr warranty. NEW fence(conects to next door neighbor.  A MUST SEE !!!!!!!!!!
